  <description type="morphology">Branchlets red-brown, turning brown in following year. Leaves: petiole 4–7 mm; blade apex rounded to obtuse, usually minutely apiculate. Bracteoles 2, deciduous, linear to oblong, small, petaloid. Pedicels 3–11 mm, proximal bract leaflike, other reduced. Flowers: sepals 2.1–3 mm; petals 12–20 mm; anthers 0.8–1.4 mm.</description>
